{
  "id": "adv_card_suz_01_03",
  "title": "成宮すず 3話 差出人不明の荷物",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_03-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、いるかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san? Are you there?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "どうしたんだ、すず？\n元気がないみたいだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What’s the matter‚ Suzu?\nYou don’t look well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.612277169454665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_03-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことありませんわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s not it at all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.881541776657104,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_03-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "ただ……スーパーの営業を増やしたので\n少し疲れているかもしれませんわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But… I’ve been doing more works\nso maybe I’m a bit tired.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.448215244798105,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_03-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "私、お仕事があれほど大変だなんて\n思いもしませんでしたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I had no idea the works\nwould be that tough.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.064663674213275,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そうか、あまり無理はするんじゃないぞ\nそういえば、なぜ仕事を増やす気になったんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ you mustn’t overdo it.\nBy the way‚ what made you want to increase your workload?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.701700711250304,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_03-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "……それは……その\n買いたいものがあったからですわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I…\nBecause there’s something I want to buy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.047300601005546,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "買いたいもの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Something you want to buy?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.680633934338886,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_03-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "……もうすぐ分かりますわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’ll know soon.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.21698311169942,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_chime-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1899.9999761581705,
          "startTime": 39.11698308785759
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "あっ誰か来たみたいだ\nすまない、ちょっと行ってくる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ looks like someone’s at the door.\nSorry‚ back in a minute.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.742134225368495,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_03-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、どうぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sure‚ go ahead.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.51734581788381,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（訪問者は、俺宛ての荷物を持った宅配業者だった）\n（荷物の差出人は、不明だ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(The visitor was a home delivery driver with a package addressed to me.)\n(It doesn’t say who sent it.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.98401248455048,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_03-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "何をぼーっとしているんですの\nさっさと開けたらいいでしょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are you just staring at?\nGo on and open it already.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.98401248455047,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "え、でも大丈夫かな\n大人が入るくらい大きい箱だし、異様に重いし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you sure about this?\nIt’s a box big enough to hold an adult‚ and it’s oddly heavy…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.05872900485991,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_03-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫ですわ！　私が保証します\nさあさあ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s fine! I promise you.\nCome on.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.09206233819323,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（荷物の中身は、オフィス用の椅子だった）\n（「いくら座っても疲れない」と評判になっているものだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(There was an office chair in the package.)\n(It has a good reputation as “the chair that won’t tire you‚ however long you sit.”)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.50046431265375,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "これは、どういうことだろう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What’s this about?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.27515829885655,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_03-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "まったくリアクションが薄いですわ。もっと\n「こんな椅子俺にはもったいない」とかありませんの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s not much of a reaction. How about\n“this chair’s too good for me” or something?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.37515839422397,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_03-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "ほら、箱のふたの裏に\n手紙が付いているみたいですわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh look‚ there’s a letter\nstuck to the back of the box cover.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.34182506089061,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "一体誰が……？\nそれよりも本当に俺宛ての荷物なのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Who’d do something like that…?\nAnd was this package really supposed to be for me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.30849172755728,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_03-suz012.m4a",
      "text": "もう！　じれったいですわね\n私が読んで差し上げます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow‚ this is getting so annoying!\nI’ll read it for you!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.74182506089056,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2565.2298736572307,
          "startTime": 104.30705493454779
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_03-suz013.m4a",
      "text": "『突然で驚いたことでしょう\nこの椅子は私からのプレゼントですわ』",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“I bet this comes as a surprise to you.\nThis chair is a present from me.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.74038826788104,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_03-suz014.m4a",
      "text": "『こういう形で渡す方が驚くと思って\n少々手の込んだ贈り方をしてみました』",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“I gave it to you this way because\nI thought it would be a bigger surprise.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.55608727505886,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_03-suz015.m4a",
      "text": "『それに、直接口で言わないぶん\nいつもより素直に、言葉が出てくると思いましたの』",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“And I thought I’d be able to be more frank with you this way\nthan speaking to you directly.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.15608727505894,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_03-suz016.m4a",
      "text": "『{user}さん、いつも私を\n支えて、見守って下さり、ありがとうございます』",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“{user}-san‚ thank you for always\nsupporting and looking out for me.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.2402178409956,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_03-suz017.m4a",
      "text": "『いつもお忙しそうにしているので、少しでも\n楽になるように、このイスを贈らせていただきます』",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“You always seem to be so busy‚\nso I’m giving you this chair to make your work a little easier.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.3068845076627,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_03-suz018.m4a",
      "text": "『これからもよろしくお願いします\n私の、マネージャーさん』",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“Please keep on looking out for me‚\nmy manager.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.09658355347995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_03-suz019.m4a",
      "text": "ふふん、ようやく気付いたのですわね\nそう、送り主の正体は……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hee hee‚ you’re starting to catch on at last.\nIndeed‚ the mystery sender is…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.16325022014655,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "一体誰からのプレゼントなんだ……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Who on Earth could have given me this present?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.26279047020128,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_03-suz020.m4a",
      "text": "え",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.55344799049547,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_01_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "ほら。手紙に名前が書いていない\n内容から察するに、星見プロの誰かかな？",
